rows.label: qst700904_msg0001
rows.name:
Thank you for your hard work!
So? Did you find anything?

rows.label: qst700904_msg0002
rows.name:
We found some footprints
that looked right, but we
lost them along the way.

rows.label: qst700904_msg0003
rows.name:
Um, what you saw probably
wasn't human, but a monster...

rows.label: qst700904_msg0004
rows.name: Oh? Over there... isn't that someone?

rows.label: qst700904_msg0006
rows.name:
I-I won't fall for that again.
There are no ghosts...

rows.label: qst700904_msg0012
rows.name:
Leave it to me. I'm
confident in my strength.

rows.label: qst700904_msg0014
rows.name:
I'll leave it to you for a while.
Don't you dare die on me!
